 />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有無邊間鋪整電腦可靠 價錢合理就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我部電腦都係搞到依加都未搞掂</blockquote><br />\n好灰 無得打機事小...要整先煩<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n你mouse無著燈？<br />\n我有著燈 <br />\n打算試多次抆ram同底版電<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa468a9dfd7ee2b06d0f8c065824e3efa3a4916","tid":320214,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n個mon插落on board卡同display card都係無畫面"},{"pid":"1bfee8b96f105b0f61e5d2007379e3d5bb404166","tid":320214,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d7e7ba86917659256c1b7b19573a9fca623143","tid":320214,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有<br />\n個mon插落on board卡同display card都係無畫面</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁，但我mouse 冇著燈"},{"pid":"2597a9dc0690d91c496f9d29b61d9f914717d2b8","tid":320214,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打諗住托部機落樓定搵上門"},{"pid":"b8e65c754e3e72df74e18c3aad38f8c2992b7415","tid":320214,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打諗住托部機落樓定搵上門</blockq